<p><strong>GA4 setup checklist:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>[ ] Create property and install tracking code</li>
<li>[ ] Configure data retention to 14 months</li>
<li>[ ] Set up internal traffic filters</li>
<li>[ ] Define conversion events for email signup, demo request, trial start</li>
<li>[ ] Link to Google Search Console</li>
<li>[ ] Enable enhanced measurement for scroll and outbound clicks</li>
</ul>
<p>Our <a href="/blog/google-analytics-4-setup/">Google Analytics 4 setup guide</a> covers each step in detail.</p>
<p><strong>Search Console setup checklist:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>[ ] Verify property ownership</li>
<li>[ ] Submit sitemap</li>
